        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>to a plate</p><p>Crack the<strong> egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into a shallow bowl and whisk</p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a separate large bowl with a  pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix it up</p>",
      "order": 4,
