    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the <strong>tilapia fillets</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add to the <strong>beaten egg</strong> and finally press it into the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to coat everything evenly – this is your <strong>breaded tilapia</strong></p>",
